Privacy Policy
1. Introduction
Welcome to Beat Swiper. This privacy policy describes how we collect, use, and share information about you when you use our game and related services (collectively, the "Services").
2. Information We Collect
2.1 Information You Provide to Us
We do not collect personal information such as names, email addresses, usernames, or passwords.
2.2 Information We Collect Automatically
When you use our Services, we automatically collect certain information, including:
Device information (e.g., operating system, device identifiers) to suggest a better experience considering your device performance.
Usage information (e.g., game progress, scores) to enhance your experience and suggest better songs for you.
3. How We Use Your Information
We use the information we collect to:
Provide and improve our Services
Personalize your experience
Monitor and analyze trends, usage, and activities
Ensure the security of our Services
Show advertisements through third-party services like AppLovin
The main goal of collecting this information is to enhance your experience by suggesting better songs and modes, and to make informed decisions on which songs and features to add based on user preferences.
4. Sharing Your Information
We may share your information with:
Service providers who perform services on our behalf, such as AppLovin for showing advertisements. We do not share information such as your age or other personal details.
We do not share your information with other players or with law enforcement, government authorities, or other third parties unless required by law.
5. Your Choices
You have certain choices regarding your information, including:
Opting out of receiving promotional communications
6. Security
We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure.
7. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this privacy policy from time to time. If we make changes, we will notify you by revising the effective date at the top of this policy.
8. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at
contact@beatswiper.com
.
9. In-App Purchases and Subscriptions
Our game offers in-app purchases and subscriptions. Upon subscribing, youâ€™ll immediately unlock all songs, remove the advertising, and get unlimited lives. You can choose a subscription plan according to price and duration. The subscriptions are $2.99 per week, $5.99 per month, and $29.99 per year, or equivalent price in your local currency. When you confirm your purchase, the payment will be charged to your account. Please cancel the automatic renewal at least 24 hours prior to the end of the current period. Otherwise, it will automatically renew and deduct the renewal fee from the account. If you cancel your subscription, you will lose all the privileges described above.